data.name: On this Magical Day Christmas Eve, I would Like to share an AMAZING SECRET with Everyone about the Dedicated and very Rewarding Journey I have been taking for Five Years to Improve my Life and my Health!!! I always had to wear Glasses since I was 12 years old, my vision was so bad I could not see clearly more than 12 inches away (Everything was always extremely blurry and very Fuzzy). On my journey to Healing my body i met an amazing teacher his name is@Arthur Haines. He taught me so much about Nutrition and for the first time in my Life my vision is coming back, last week i started seeing letters clearly about 2 feet away, now i can see about six feet away, and when I'm a passenger in a car, I can read Billboard Signs (I was never able to see the Words on Billboards Before becasue they were much too Blurry, it's Truly a Miracle), my vision has been improving so much, and i'm slowly gaining back my strength back, my weight, my ambition, and my Life. Thank you with all my heart Arthur Haines and everyone who has helped me on my path to recovery, you are all Angels and I cherish the time you dedicated to educate me with all my heart ♥ I promise to carry your Wisdom to Everyone I meet to help others become empowered and healthier. PLEASE LIKE my AMAZING FRIEND Arthur's Facebook Page he is a GREAT TEACHER someone I truly Respect and Look up to. If it wasn't for Arthur and all the Amazing Friends and Nutrition Experts I met who Helped me learn so much about Nutrition on my quest for Healing, I don't know if I would be here today sharing this Incredible story with you. Thank you for all your Love and Support ♥ Sending my Blessing to all ♥ MERRY CHRISTMAS!!! HUGS and LOVE ~Mariana Roberts
